  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Content Creator",
  "description": "<h1>Business Content Creator</h1><p><strong>Business Content Creator (Video)</strong><br />(Full-time / Contract)</p><h2>About the Role</h2><p>We are looking for a <strong>Business Content Creator</strong> who can create compelling, educational, and inspiring business-focused videos across short-form and long-form formats.</p><p>Your job is to <strong>translate real business insights, founder stories, and strategic thinking into content that people actually finish watching</strong>.</p><p>This role sits at the intersection of <strong>content, storytelling, and business literacy</strong>.</p><h2>Key Responsibilities</h2><h3>Content Creation & Storytelling</h3><ul><li><p>Create business-focused video content (short-form & long-form)</p></li><li><p>Develop clear narratives around entrepreneurship, leadership, sales, mindset, and growth</p></li><li><p>Break down complex business ideas into simple, engaging stories</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with hosts/interviewees to bring out strong insights</p></li></ul><h3>Filming & Production</h3><ul><li><p>Film videos using phone</p></li><li><p>Ensure clean framing, lighting, and audio</p></li><li><p>Capture b-roll when needed to enhance storytelling</p></li></ul><h3>Post-Production</h3><ul><li><p>Amend storytelling and captions delivered from editor's team enhancing video quality.</p></li><li><p>Follow brand style, tone, and visual guidelines</p></li></ul><h3>Platform & Performance Awareness</h3><ul><li><p>Understand what performs well on business content platforms</p></li><li><p>Optimise hooks, openings, and structure for watch time</p></li><li><p>Iterate content based on performance feedback</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><h3>Skills & Experience</h3><ul><li><p>Experience creating video content (portfolio required)</p></li><li><p>Strong sense of storytelling and pacing</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with editing tools (CapCut)</p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of business, entrepreneurship, or personal development</p></li><li><p>Able to take feedback and iterate quickly</p></li></ul><h3>Mindset & Traits</h3><ul><li><p>Curious about how businesses work</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented but fast-moving</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated and disciplined</p></li><li><p>Comfortable experimenting with formats and ideas</p></li><li><p>Willing to learn and improve continuously</p></li></ul><h2>Bonus If You Have</h2><ul><li><p>Experience creating business, finance, or educational content</p></li><li><p>Copywriting or scripting ability</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with analytics and content performance metrics</p></li></ul><h2>Performance Expectations</h2><ul><li><p>Consistent content output</p></li><li><p>Strong storytelling and clarity</p></li><li><p>Ability to improve retention and engagement over time</p></li><li><p>Reliability in deadlines and revisions</p></li></ul><h2>Why Join Us</h2><ul><li><p>Create content that educates and inspires entrepreneurs</p></li><li><p>Work closely with founders, leaders, and decision-makers</p></li><li><p>High creative ownership and growth potential</p></li><li><p>Clear feedback loops and performance-based progression</p></li></ul><h2>Growth Path</h2><ul><li><p>Senior Content Creator</p></li><li><p>Lead Editor / Content Lead</p></li><li><p>Creative Director (Business Content)</p></li></ul>",
